        %h1 theDocs
        %p
          %strong theDocs
          is a html online documentation template which can help you rapidly develop your next software's documentation. It can be used for documenting API, frameworks, plugins, templates, etc. It's based on Bootstrap and contains a lot of components to easily make your interactive documentation.
        %p
          %b theDocs
          comes with a simple design and puts its focus on readability and functionality. It has a lot of useful components to reduce the burden of writing a documentation for your next product. With the help of
          %b theDocs
          just focus on the quality of writing; don't worry about the quality of design and ease of writing. We guarantee them!
